Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: python3, python3-gi, python3-passlib, gir1.2-gtk-4.0, gir1.2-adw-1, ansible, sshpass
Maintainer: Indrek
Description: Game server deployment and monitoring tool
 GSDeploy is a GTK4 desktop application for deploying and monitoring
 game servers on virtual machines using Ansible and Docker.
